				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Sounds alot like the con system from City of Heroes. Its essentially the same thing. You fought thugs in groups, and in the groups there could be any of the 3 "tiers". FOr example...A group of 7 thugs could consist of 4 minions (weakest), 2 Lieutenants, and a Boss. A minion your level would con even, liuetenants yellow and bosses red. It was actually a good system...even if the game was only good for the 30 day trial =P
